Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:08.61,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Open your eyes. You'll get in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:13.63,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:17.88,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we'll try running\Nto the river in Tamagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:19.68,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I want to determine everyone's level,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:21.75,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,so I can plan your practice\Nschedules for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:22.89,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:26.90,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:31.49,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,After all that, you're still participating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:34.42,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Just for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:38.60,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're some kind of freak, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:41.82,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing beats eating after a run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:42.56,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:44.56,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.21,0:00:46.18,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:49.27,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Tamagawa? {\i1}That{\i0} Tamagawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:01:00.53,Why?(ep 03),TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Why
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:51.60,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that Tamagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:54.34,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that five kilometers away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:00:57.37,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You're really familiar\Nwith the local geography.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.37,0:00:58.14,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:00.53,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:01.98,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,That's five kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:06.00,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Five kilometers one way \Nmeans ten kilometers round trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:07.58,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Ten kilometers first thing in the morning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:11.42,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,If you can shout that much\Nafter waking up, you'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:12.54,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:14.86,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:26.60,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.93,0:01:31.77,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Start at your own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:33.34,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:40.20,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Where is your dignity?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:43.79,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Where has your human dignity gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:48.34,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,We're allowing ourselves to be\Nforced to run without objection.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:51.63,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really call ourselves people?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:55.89,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:26.97,Series_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Run with the Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:37.36,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yay. I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.36,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,What? It was a tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.62,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,I beat you by a hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:51.39,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:55.61,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've wanted\Nto go back to my home country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:10.52,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The theory will come later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:15.40,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,First, your body needs to experience\Nfirsthand how far five kilometers is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:17.29,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you'll surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:23.40,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,B-Butterfly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:32.58,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You'll surely be able to run it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:42.17,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.68,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Breakfast is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.77,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back as a butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:51.39,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NYou're not making any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.29,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.09,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:58.06,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:00.83,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Is he ever going to stop running?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.77,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Your body gets cold if you just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:10.64,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:18.73,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand now \Njust how stupid your idea is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:22.52,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,They just ran a mere five kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:27.14,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Every section of the Hakone\NEkiden is at least 20 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:28.39,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,That's more than quadruple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:34.27,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to race that distance against\Nrunners who have endured intense training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:40.28,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,We could practice for \Nten years and still be behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:47.09,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,Just how insane is his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:48.77,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,He's not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:52.99,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It won't take ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:56.96,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,After all, there's less than\Nten months until the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.42,Ep_title,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,A Single Flower
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:10.61,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,At universities that participate\Nin the Hakone Ekiden,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:15.17,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,everyone runs 5,000 meters\Nin less than about 14:30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:18.73,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll consider that one of our goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:21.52,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what that looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:24.95,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,The simple calculation is less\Nthan three minutes per kilometer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:26.04,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:29.73,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,One kilometer in the time\Nit takes to prepare cup noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:32.20,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it harder to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:36.16,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,He means it's inhumanly fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.87,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,I bet there are lots of guys like\Nthat where you're from, Musa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:42.08,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,More prejudice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:46.34,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,My high school's long distance\Nrace was only three kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.47,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.43,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:54.16,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You're right that it's not \Nan easy speed to achieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:58.06,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,But if you don't know what \Nyour goals are, you can't aim for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.18,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:04.92,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,If you do the required training, it's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:08.03,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll limit our focus to Hakone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:10.40,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That dramatically improves our chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:13.01,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,On what basis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:17.24,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,On what basis are you making those claims?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:20.00,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.99,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to owe any favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.88,Day(ep 03),TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(530,1)}Day 2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.44,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,They ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:44.11,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wake them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:45.90,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki never came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:47.29,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.96,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,He went clubbing as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:53.85,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Clubbing sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:56.01,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,I bet there are lots of cute girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:58.16,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to ask him to take us with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:00.27,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:02.55,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.30,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kurahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:34.48,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:37.66,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.38,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.26,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't done that since grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:57.01,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a Kansei Uni student?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:57.81,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:08:59.88,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,On the Kansei Uni track and field team?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.04,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:03.48,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Haiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:06.42,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you familiar with Kiyose Haiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:07.59,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.95,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:35.34,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.28,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Haiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.70,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What about school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:40.77,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,After this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:43.52,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I came first thing, but no one was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.85,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We're still slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.02,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:50.48,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him if he was \Non the track and field team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:53.02,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see anyone else who could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.08,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.65,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't ignore her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:05.14,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Yaokatsu girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:05.93,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:09.79,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Yaokatsu. She's the daughter of the\Nvegetable vendor in the shopping center.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.97,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are they dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:14.39,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:16.98,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,A high school girl's a little too young.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.34,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Let's get back to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:21.15,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.72,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Practice hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:27.28,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,We will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:42.74,main,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow! Then your future is secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:45.62,main,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'll have to call you\Nfor help if I'm ever on trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:48.58,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'd totally be down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.54,main,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,You might be on trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.07,main,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,You never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:55.09,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Can I get your number, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:58.05,main,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be hilarious if this were a scam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.53,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.84,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I'll get your number, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:03.51,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.62,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:13.10,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:14.49,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. My ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:18.70,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing. I don't know how\Nyou can stay in there for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:19.85,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're wasting your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:20.56,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:22.05,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're wasting your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:25.65,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any reason to run\Nor anything to gain from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:28.83,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to create memories\Nor network with you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:34.53,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,This year of freedom\Nis my well-deserved reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:37.40,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I deserve to savor this vacation from life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:40.12,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're wasting your time\Nby trying to convince me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:42.30,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a total waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.59,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I have a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:47.60,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't run in the Hakone\NEkiden without ten members.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:51.27,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't exist for your purposes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.10,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:58.10,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I don't intend to unilaterally\Nimpose my will on you, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:11:59.49,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:00.40,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:01.11,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.36,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:06.12,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's not fair to just\Nmake you accompany me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:11.86,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's very important for teammates\Nto respect and understand one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.67,Day(ep 03),TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(530,1)}Day 3
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:25.14,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. I'm finding a way out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:26.64,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:33.10,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,She's Yaokatsu's daughter,\N Katsuta Hanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.06,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be helping us sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:36.71,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I've got school,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:40.13,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,so I can only help out early\Nin the morning and late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:42.03,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:43.54,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.50,Why?(ep 03),TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Why
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.87,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a grand sight when everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:05.56,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kurahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:09.45,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I want to time everyone's finish. Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.81,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:19.48,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to go crazy\Njust because I'm timing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:24.75,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I just want data to plan our practices.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:30.16,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm timing today's run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:34.82,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:38.24,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell Hana to keep an eye out for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:00.89,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Haiji's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:02.69,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,The details are unclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:06.70,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Being forced to run is already\Na human rights violation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.51,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,and now he's showing off his girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:11.30,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Just how much does he intend to toy with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:15.16,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,But it's clear now that King\Nhas some hidden potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.64,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:20.42,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no matter how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:31.75,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Well? I wasn't lying, was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:33.50,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:35.74,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:41.35,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Work hard, and women will approach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:43.78,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It only took three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:47.86,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep getting stronger\Nand attract more attention...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:53.95,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Haiji, we're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:57.13,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,We doubted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:15:01.75,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,We thought you were tricking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:06.01,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,But it was true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:11.97,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's only Yaokatsu's Hana so far,\Nbut as long as we work hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:14.07,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:20.18,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,On the other side of the road\Nare more women than you can count!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.73,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.64,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,We decided to attend college...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.75,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,They've been fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:32.68,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,They sure have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:35.92,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's aim for the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:38.54,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,What? What if we actually win?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:40.00,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:41.71,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have your hands full.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.83,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The mountains of Hakone\Nare the steepest in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:48.34,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what that means!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:50.67,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,But it's so intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:51.98,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The mountains of Hakone are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:53.34,main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,The steepest in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:54.79,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The mountains of Hakone are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:55.96,main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,The steepest in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:55.94,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Musa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:56.85,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:16:00.80,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about continuing a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:02.46,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:05.60,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they be fooled so easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:09.73,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? I thought you\Nwere going to make him give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:12.54,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're on board now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.20,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:22.16,Why?(ep 03),TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Why
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:18.59,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Prince can't even finish properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:21.61,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,No one would believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.92,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:29.84,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,So why is he so confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:35.76,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head back! Time for breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.61,Yaokatsu_17:34(Ep 03),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Yaokatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:50.28,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do good this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.90,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:56.14,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Athletes perform better\Nin front of an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:17:00.45,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. It really was fun, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:01.95,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:04.91,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's effective, even if all\Nyou're doing is watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:07.92,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I hope your dream comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.18,main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,It will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:09.88,main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:11.95,main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,He's been waiting four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:13.88,main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some good members, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:17.30,main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she couldn't keep up on her bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.82,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:22.56,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kurahara famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:25.06,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.32,main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I'm excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:32.03,main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know if there's\Nanything we can do to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:33.64,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:37.49,Tsuru-no-yu_17:34(Ep 03),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuru-no-yu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:40.39,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,What? Qualifier?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.91,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Joji, your bubbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:46.36,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Most people only know about the actual race.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:50.11,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,I just learned about it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:53.06,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Of the twenty schools that participate\Nin the Hakone Ekiden,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:56.83,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,aside from the ten seeded teams\Nthat qualify the previous year,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:18:01.35,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,they have to participate\Nin a preliminary qualifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:02.96,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:07.36,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll race in that first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:08.35,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:11.77,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,We still don't know if we'll be racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:16.59,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,How many schools participate in the qualifier?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:19.02,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,About fifty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:21.55,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,So only the top fifth qualify.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.11,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,I bet we can do it if we try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:26.44,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Haiji said we're just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:30.19,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,We can do it as long as we practice hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:31.44,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:39.59,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,How hard do you think they\Npractice to be in the top fifth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:43.85,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,And not everyone can\Nparticipate in the qualifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:48.90,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Each athlete needs an official record\Nof finishing 5,000 meters in less than 16:30
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:52.19,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,or 10,000 in 30:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:56.73,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Those are astronomical figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:19:00.74,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,You have to achieve those\Nrecords before the qualifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:04.33,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if you have\Na couple of fast guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:07.28,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has to be running at a high level.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:13.63,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,An amateur who can't even finish\Nten kilometers shouldn't be aiming for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:18.10,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand how reckless he's being?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:21.02,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:22.95,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Then stop wasting your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:23.76,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:26.26,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,What's your deal, Kakeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.32,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.99,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. What are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:32.06,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,You're fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.00,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:36.13,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're worried about us,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.19,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,but we're the ones doing the work, so who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.95,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Run with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:53.20,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I don't work well with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.82,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kurahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:14.56,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,He left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:17.64,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,We only ran together for one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:19.53,main,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:38.48,flashback,TWIN,0000,0000,0000,,Run with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:42.87,main,BOY,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:56.19,main,BOY,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Kurahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.65,0:22:42.97,main,NARRATION,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "Shadows That Don't Fade."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:45.51,Next_Time,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(524,1)}Next Time:{\fs16} Shadows That Don't Fade
